This document provides a complete beginner-friendly, end-to-end RAG (Retrieval Augmented Generation)
project using Node.js + Express (backend) and React (frontend).
1️⃣ What We Are Building
Project: Ask-My-PDF (RAG App)
What it does: - Upload a PDF - Ask questions related to that PDF - AI answers only from the uploaded
content
Core Concepts Used: - RAG pipeline (Ingestion + Query) - Embeddings - Vector Database (Chroma – local) -
OpenAI LLM
2️⃣ Prerequisites
Make sure you have: - Node.js v18+ - npm - OpenAI API Key
